entries.category: The Clone Relics, Fist of the Empire
entries.journal_entry_description: You stumbled upon classified Rebel data. Things can only get better from here on... or can they?
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: The datapad you found seem to contain Rebel attack plans on Imperial and Trandoshan structures on the planet of Kashyyyk. You should probably bring this to a high ranking Imperial officer on that planet immediately.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Admiral Krieg has ordered some new hardware and need you to bring it back to the base. Travel on the road east of Kachirho until you reach a large gate. The AT-ST will be dropped off there, so you can escort it back to the base.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Return to Admiral Krieg and explain yourself soldier!
entries.task03_journal_entry_title: Return to Admiral Krieg and explain yourself soldier!
entries.task08_journal_entry_description: Return to base with the AT-ST. Stay sharp. Kashyyyk is dangerous, Rebels or not.
entries.task09_journal_entry_description: Good job soldier, return to Admiral Krieg and see what he has planned next.
